title: The top iPhone and iPad apps on App Store
text:
App Store Official Charts for the week ending October 18, 2015:

1. Minecraft: Story Mode, Telltale Inc
2. Minecraft: Pocket Edition, Mojang
3. Plague Inc., Ndemic Creations
4. Geometry Dash, RobTop Games AB
5. Heads Up!, Warner Bros.
6. NBA 2K16, 2K
7. Scribblenauts Remix, Warner Bros.
8. Bloons TD 5, Ninja Kiwi
9. PewDiePie: Legend of the Brofist, Outerminds Inc.
10. THE GAME OF LIFE Classic Edition, Electronic Arts

2. The Walking Dead: No Man's Land, Next Games Oy
